<HEADLINE>
FT  11 JAN 94 / Coach holiday company fails
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Charter Coach Holidays, of Harwich, Essex, which specialised in UK and
short-haul European trips, collapsed yesterday. The company was covered by
the Bus and Coach Council holiday bond scheme. The council said it would
honour all valid claims in respect of full payment or deposits taken for
holidays with Charter Coach up to December 31.
